parameters: \unknown\lspi[50]Feeling a bit out of your element,\. boy?\|\^
\lyonHiding in the shadows?\.\.\. Are you scared?\|\^
\unknown\lspi[50]Ha\.ha\.ha!\.\.\. You have spunk,\.\. I'll give you that.\|\^
\lyonDammit\..\..\.. \.I can't see a thing in this darkness.\.\.\.\.\^
\lyonBut\..\..\..\. What if I took his darkness away?\|\^
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]The power of fire?\. Now that\..\..\..\. That I did not expect!
\lyonWhat are you going to do now without the shadows?
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]Apparently I will have a bit more fun than anticipated!
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]... noticed that you are nothing but an insect beneath my boot.
\lyonHe's\..\..\.. not even broken a sweat.\| How could\.-\.-\^
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]I must say\., this has been fun.
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]I have not seen one with such an interesting combat style before.
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]A shame you had no chance to develop these skills of yours.\. Perhaps you would have been a worthy opponent.
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]Sorry?\. You are going to have to speak up.
\lyonI swore on the names of my parents I would not let this town fall\..\..\..
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]Oh well.\.\.\. Someone needs to clean up this mess\..\..\..
\n<Bandit Leader>\lspi[50]His hair is\..\..\..  Wait\..\..\.. Could he be?
